title: Iran's state-run IRNA news agency, citing negotiator, says Tehran will start enriching uranium to 60% purity
body: Iran's state-run IRNA news agency, citing negotiator, says Tehran will start enriching uranium to 60% purityDUBAI, United Arab Emirates -- Iran's state-run IRNA news agency, citing negotiator, says Tehran will start enriching uranium to 60% purity.
